{"tid":834334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒店房食榴槤被男友拒絕 女子掟榴槤施襲謊稱遭強姦","createTime":"2018-09-24T06:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T07:45:02.000Z","uid":80516,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa22d8a3d7fcbaa34a6dafcea39f4036bc523bbd","tid":834334,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:45:09.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】浙江一名29歲張姓女子報稱在酒店遭同齡男友強姦，報警求助。據了解，張女主動與男友前往酒店「度春宵」，事後因肚餓要求吃榴槤被拒，盛怒之下手持榴槤襲擊男友，男友還擊。張女最終因涉謊報警情和擾亂公共秩序，被警方處以行政拘留5日。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，張女與男友本來關係親暱，而且結婚在即。事發當晚，兩人前往酒店「度春宵」。據了解，張女當晚前往酒店前，預先買了一個榴槤，打算在酒店房進食，但男友希望她回家吃。張女聞訊後相當不滿，把榴槤砸向男友洩憤，兩人隨即爆發肢體衝突，張女則在打完架後，報警謊稱自己遭到性侵。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報後，立刻趕到酒店現場調查，但發現房間內部相當整齊，毫無性侵或任何衝突痕迹，在追問下，張女坦承是因吃榴槤被拒，暴怒之下施襲，又指自己擔心如實報稱情侶打架，警方未必會重視，故選擇誇大案情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/144323_40697c7c3d5890eec0e515cfe89a5bc8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F144323_40697c7c3d5890eec0e515cfe89a5bc8.jpeg&h=9f500e78&s={SIZE}\" />張女被警員帶走。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/144359_2898334795ffc02ac99495e6299a9ae3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F144359_2898334795ffc02ac99495e6299a9ae3.jpeg&h=67da8598&s={SIZE}\" />張女（左）盛怒之下，手持榴槤襲擊男友（右）。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"02adea42808a13e9d8988b8169e7fc299e84e850","tid":834334,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"佢塊西仲臭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097d3b0809efed704625b443a23e6cd67d9a8f86","tid":834334,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:50:14.000Z","msg":"為咗食榴槤，依家婚都未必結得成，何必呢"},{"pid":"0f024c37858b5d849360d956e3fb22443da677a1","tid":834334,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"我睇左d乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3b12740d545058b006865c91b33844580990ce","tid":834334,"uid":200474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c28a5828f4f249b44b19e312a6aa03274d6bbe","tid":834334,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"榴槤咁大吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fa180eac9878cd68b86ff1d0a467a06e1a6d77","tid":834334,"uid":211716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"召喚女權撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ba67f589bcf57f410aacd06e52fb7ad202da5a","tid":834334,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c34beaf611d0f227a983a4d326d4eb1c471785b2","tid":834334,"uid":78522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"榴槤乜乜乜"},{"pid":"40fc3bd90e89ccf8bb529ce6cf4b187b115b34e6","tid":834334,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3ba67f589bcf57f410aacd06e52fb7ad202da5a","tid":834334,"uid":128223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:45:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會係報左警 啲公安身上有cam影到"}]}